body_html:
May be the hdf5 reader prefer to read from a single huge hdf5 file, instead of a file-name queue.
The bioinformatics data often stores in one mat/gtcx/hdf5 file.
However, open it with h5py.File as numpy array and feed the tf.placeholder is OK for now.
